com.mousebird.maply

Class MapboxVectorTileParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mousebird.maply.MapboxVectorTileParser

  • public class MapboxVectorTileParser
extends java.lang.Object
    This object parses Mapbox Vector Tile format one tile at a time. Set it up and then ask it to parse the given blob of data into vector objects.
    Just supports vector data for now.
